\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔鳩該你睇吓美國彈劾嘅程序同歷史先喺度廢啦, 好嗎? 係有槍炮呀, 但係唔鳩該讀撚晒成段2nd amendment先吠啦好無? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個完全唔理解咩時候可以用彈劾, 咩時候用投票, 咩時候&quot;推翻自己唔承認既總統&quot;再次證明你係應該讀多啲書先好衝出嚟柒. 點醒你就意為屌緊你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算係屌, 都係屌緊你個無知同邏輯. 無其他.<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味自己睇返HRC大選前2 個禮拜民調, Comey出手救Trump後, 大選前3-7日民調, 再睇選舉日HRC贏幾多popular votes先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後自己睇而家嘅民調 同 上屆民調嘅%先講啦. 唉. 真係點醒部牆都快過點醒唔願醒嘅人. 慘撚情"},{"pid":"3f466fd339a1146c46247d91a0686520389c08c8","tid":1554131,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iD7C3F3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD7C3F3.png&h=7d8980df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbf4f555afebdfab0a2bb3da8b9e9ce80093c413","tid":1554131,"uid":2140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f466fd339a1146c46247d91a0686520389c08c8","tid":1554131,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iD7C3F3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD7C3F3.png&h=7d8980df&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"你個人都幾厚面皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VamoZB6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVamoZB6.png&h=4cae57d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13bb605cf9053414fda0c6c8aa65fbc8dd5a7455","tid":1554131,"uid":2140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ced99f55527906e26bebf